lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur may be licking their wounds after crashing out of the Champions League but they must quickly refocus as they return to Premier League action on Saturday at leaders Chelsea in their third straight London derby.

headline.print_headline: Spurs Back in Derby Mode at Chelsea After Euro Exit
